Mokonzi ya ba Maï-Maï Simba mpe babundi na ye motoba bakufi na bitumba na mapinga ya FARDC na etuka ya Ituri, eyebisi molobeli ya mapinga na esika liye. 
 "Tosukisi basimba minduki sambo, kati na bango mokambi na bango Manu," elobi lieutenant Jules Tshikudi ya FARDC.
Bitumba liye lisalamaki o’mokolo mwa yambo moleki, na kati na butu.





 


Lire aussi :


Pene na 850 bato bakufi na Yumbi






"Bavandi bisika liye basepeli na koyoka liwa ya Manu, mokonzi ya batomboki oyo aminisa bango pasi," ebakisi Lieut. Tshikudi.
Nkombo ya solo ya Manu eyebani te, kasi akitanaki na Paul Sadala, alias Morgan, oyo bamobomaki na 2014. Ye afundamaki na kosalaka bokila oyo epekisama.